caption: Nova Vex, a cyberpunk goddess of the night, prowls neon-drenched alleyways with a confident swagger that makes even the rain shimmer. With a low-angle shot, she glides through the rain-soaked streets, her body lit in electric blue and magenta neon. Her gaze is bold, her confidence is a whisper of mystery, as she holds a holographic drone that glows against the skyline. ⚡💫 #cyberpunk #futurism #streetfashion #digitalart #neonaesthetics
